# Multi-Role Architecture & UX Overhaul

Major restructuring of the PMS app: consolidating to clinic-only registration, adding receptionist accounts, reworking role-based access control, and improving navigation UX.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **PocketBase schema change required.** A new `receptionists` collection must be created in PocketBase with fields: `username`, `password`, `name`, `phone`, `clinic` (relation â†’ clinics). This is needed before the app can log in receptionists.

> [!WARNING]
> **Breaking change:** All existing "Register as Doctor" / invite-code flows will be removed. Doctors can only be created through a clinic account (during registration or from the settings/profile page). Existing standalone doctor accounts will still work for login, but no new ones can be created through the app UI.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Receptionist PocketBase collection:** A `receptionists` auth collection is needed. Fields: `username` (text, unique), `password`, `name` (text), `phone` (text, optional), `clinic` (relation â†’ clinics), `is_active` (bool, default true). API rules should restrict receptionists to read-only access on patients and full access on appointments within their clinic.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Auth & Registration Restructuring

#### A. Remove Doctor Self-Registration

##### [DELETE] [role_selection_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/screens/role_selection_screen.dart)
- The "Create Account" screen with "Register as Clinic" / "Register as Doctor" cards is no longer needed.
- The "Register" link on the login page will navigate directly to `/register/clinic` (Step 1).

##### [DELETE] [doctor_registration_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/screens/doctor_registration/doctor_registration_screen.dart)
- The entire standalone doctor registration flow is removed.

##### [MODIFY] [login_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/screens/login_screen.dart)
- **Role toggle:** Change the two-tab toggle from `[Clinic | Doctor]` to a **three-tab** toggle: `[Clinic | Doctor | Receptionist]`.
- **Register link:** Change navigation from `/register` (RoleSelectionScreen) to `/register/clinic` directly. Update label from "Register" to "Register Clinic".
- Add `UserRole.receptionist` login path calling `_authService.loginReceptionist()`.

##### [MODIFY] [auth_service.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/auth_service.dart)
- Add `UserRole.receptionist` to the `UserRole` enum.
- Add `loginReceptionist(username, password)` method authenticating against the `receptionists` PB collection.
- Add `restoreSession()` support for `receptionist` role.
- Remove `registerDoctor()` method (no longer callable from the UI).
- Keep `loginDoctor()` since doctors still log in â€” they just get created by clinics.

##### [MODIFY] [auth_provider.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/providers/auth_provider.dart)
- Add `ReceptionistModel? receptionist` to `AuthState`.
- Add `loginReceptionist()` method.
- Remove `registerDoctor()` method.
- Update `restoreSession()` for the receptionist role.

##### [NEW] [receptionist_model.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/models/receptionist_model.dart)
- Simple model: `id`, `name`, `username`, `phone`, `clinicId`, `isActive`, `created`, `updated`.
- `fromRecord(RecordModel)` factory.

##### [MODIFY] [pb_collections.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/constants/pb_collections.dart)
- Add `static const String receptionists = 'receptionists';`.

##### [MODIFY] [app_router.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/router/app_router.dart)
- Remove `/register` route (RoleSelectionScreen).
- Remove `/register/doctor` route.
- Change "Register" link to navigate to `/register/clinic`.
- Add `/dashboard/receptionist` route.

