### Phase 2: Role-Based UI (MainLayout)

##### [MODIFY] [main_layout.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/dashboard/screens/main_layout.dart)
- Add `PageController` and replace `IndexedStack` with `PageView` for swipe-to-switch-tab animation (left/right).
- Sync `BottomNavigationBar` selection with `PageView`.
- **Clinic role:** 5 tabs â€” Home, Appointments, Analytics, Patients, Profile. (unchanged)
- **Doctor role:** 4 tabs â€” Home, Appointments, Patients, Profile. (remove Analytics â€” doctors don't need full clinic analytics)
- **Receptionist role:** 3-4 tabs â€” Home (summary dashboard), Appointments, Patients (list only, no medical details), Profile.
- Expose a way for the dashboard to programmatically switch to the Appointments tab (for the "Upcoming Today" card tap).

