## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **PocketBase `receptionists` auth collection:** Should I provide a script/instructions for creating this collection, or will you set it up manually?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 2. **Doctor login restriction:** Should doctor accounts that belong to a clinic have any restrictions (e.g., can a doctor see patients from other doctors in the same clinic?) Currently they only see their own patients. Does this remain the same?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 3. **Existing data:** There are existing doctor records that were created via the old self-registration flow. Should we keep the `loginDoctor()` functionality so those accounts can still sign in? (Plan assumes yes.)

> [!WARNING]
> 4. **Payment prep:** You mentioned doctors are paid modules. Should I add any fields or flags now (e.g., `is_trial`, `subscription_tier` on clinics, `is_paid` on doctors) to prepare for the payment system? Or defer entirely?

